latestPosts.caption:
🎉 Hurry! Registration Open for Sweta Patel’s 15-Day Basic to Advanced Makeup Course! 🎉

Join Sweta Patel for an exclusive 15-day offline makeup course that covers all bridal looks with the latest techniques and hacks, along with hands-on practice.

Course Details:
* 6 Live Makeup Demos covering Society Look, Smokey Glam, Haldi, Reception, and Bridal looks.

* Every alternate day includes a demo followed by a practice session.

Course Schedule:
* Day 1: Introduction to Makeup, Brush  Knowledge, Product Knowledge
* Day 2: Practice session
* Day 3: Demo 1 – Society Subtle Look
* Day 4: Practice session
* Day 5: Demo 2 – Smokey Glam Look
* Day 6: Practice session
* Day 7: Demo 3 – Haldi Look
* Day 8: Practice session
* Day 9: Demo 4 – Mehendi Look (Waterproof Makeup)
* Day 10: Practice session
* Day 11: Demo 5 – Reception Look (Airbrush Makeup)
* Day 12: Practice session
* Day 13: Demo 6 – Bridal Look (Tear-proof & Sweat-resistant Makeup)
* Day 14: Mature Skin Demo, Client Work Demo (Quick Makeup for Clients)
* Day 15: Social Media Knowledge, Certificate Distribution, Closing Ceremony

Important Notes:
	•	Bring your own makeup brushes and beauty blenders for practice.
	•	Models required for practice sessions.

	•	Location:
The Magic Touch by Sweta Patel
51-A2 Chitvan Bungalow, South Bopal, Ahmedabad
Date: 28th April 2025
Time: 12:30 PM onwards

📞 Call/WhatsApp: 9510608435 to book your seat now!

Limited seats available – Don’t miss out!
